name: Mobile UI Kit (Community)
description:
Power your workflow with this simple Mobile UI Kit ⚡️


The kit includes a selection of components and layouts to be used with any mobile application.


Contents:

  • Mobile components
  • Text and color styles
  • Common screen layouts


Have suggestions? Let me know! @protogeridis


This is a remix of a Mobile UI Kit by Tony Gemayel.


Made with lots of ♥️ in London.
